      "seed": 1113142730,
      "version": 410,
      "versionNonce": 1755594454,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778924411009,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "假如第二个中间件不允许往后走，\n那么会直接从第二个中间件的 process_response 返回给用户，\n不会走到视图函数。",
      "fontSize": 12.225441575360765,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "假如第二个中间件不允许往后走，\n那么会直接从第二个中间件的 process_response 返回给用户，\n不会走到视图函数。",
      "autoResize": true,
